I"йн<h1 id="lecture-03-Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓">Lecture 03 Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓</h1>

<p><strong>Е▐┌Х─┐Ф∙≥Ф²░</strong>О╪ </p>

<ul>
  <li><em>Gareth, J., Daniela, W., Trevor, H., &amp; Robert, T. (2013). An intruduction to statistical learning: with applications in R. Spinger.</em></li>
  <li><em>Hastie, T., Tibshirani, R., &amp; Friedman, J. (2009). The elements of statistical learning: data mining, inference, and prediction. Spinger Science &amp; Business Media.</em></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="1-Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓">1. Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓</h2>

<h3 id="11-Д╩─Д╧┬Ф≤╞Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓">1.1 Д╩─Д╧┬Ф≤╞Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓</h3>

<p>Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф≤╞Д╦─Г╖█Г╝─Е█∙Г └Г⌡▒Г²ёЕ╜╕Д╧═Ф√╧ФЁ∙О╪▄Е╝┐Е│┤Х╝╬ $Y$ Е▓▄ $X_1, X_2,\dots, X_p$ Д╧▀И≈╢Г └Д╬²Х╣√Е┘ЁГЁ╩Ф≤╞Г╨©Ф─╖Г └Ц─┌</p>

<p>ФЁ╗Ф└▐О╪ Г°÷Е╝·Г └Е⌡·Е╫▓Е┤╫Ф∙╟Ф╟╦Х©°Д╦█Д╪ Ф≤╞Г╨©Ф─╖Ц─┌</p>

<p><img src="http://andy-blog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/blog/2020-09-08-WX20200908-100135%402x.png" width="70%" /></p>

<center><span style="font-size:10pt"> <span style="color:steelblue;font-weight:bold">Е⌡╬ 1</span>О╪  Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀О╪▄Е┘╤Д╦╜Г╨╒Х┴╡Ф⌡╡Г╨©Х║╗Г╓╨Г°÷Е╝·Е⌡·Е╫▓Е┤╫Ф∙╟О╪▄Х⌠²Х┴╡Г⌡╢Г╨©Х║╗Г╓╨Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓Е┤╫Ф∙╟Ц─┌</span></center>

<p>Е╟╫Г╝║Г°▀Х╣╥Ф²╔Д╪╪Д╧▌Х©┤Д╨▌Г╝─Е█∙О╪▄Д╫├Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓Е°╗Ф╕┌Е©╣Д╦┼Е▓▄Е╝·Х╥╣Д╦╜И┐╫И²·Е╦╦Ф°┴Г■╗Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="12-Д╬▀Е╜░Е╧©Е▒┼Ф∙╟Ф█╝Г └Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓">1.2 Д╬▀Е╜░О╪ Е╧©Е▒┼Ф∙╟Ф█╝Г └Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓</h3>

<p>Е⌡·И║╬Д╦┼Х┼┌Х╞╬Д╦╜Г └Е╧©Е▒┼Ф∙╟Ф█╝Г └Д╬▀Е╜░О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▐╞Х┐╫Д╪ Е┘ЁЕ©┐Д╩╔Д╦▀И≈╝И╒≤О╪ </p>

<ul>
  <li>Е╧©Е▒┼И╒└Г╝≈Е▓▄И■─Е■╝И╒²Д╧▀И≈╢Ф≤╞Е░╕Ф°┴Е┘ЁГЁ╩О╪÷</li>
  <li>Е╧©Е▒┼И╒└Г╝≈Е▓▄И■─Е■╝И╒²Д╧▀И≈╢Г └Г⌡╦Е┘ЁФ─╖Ф°┴Е╓ Е╪╨О╪÷</li>
  <li>Е⌠╙Д╨⌡Е╙▓Д╫⌠Ф°┴Е┼╘Д╨▌Ф▐░Е█┤И■─Е■╝И╒²О╪÷</li>
  <li>Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е╕┌Д╫∙Е┤├Г║╝Е°╟И╒└Ф╣▀Ф°╙Ф²╔Г └И■─Е■╝И╒²О╪÷</li>
  <li>Д╨▄Х─┘Д╧▀И≈╢Г └Е┘ЁГЁ╩Ф≤╞Г╨©Ф─╖Г └Е░≈О╪÷</li>
  <li>Д╦█Е░▄Е╧©Е▒┼Е╙▓Д╫⌠Д╧▀И≈╢Ф≤╞Е░╕Е╜≤Е°╗Е█▐Е░▄Д╫°Г■╗О╪÷</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="http://andy-blog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/blog/2020-08-15-WX20200815-221610%402x.png" width="90%" /></p>

<p><span style="font-size:10pt"> <span style="color:steelblue;font-weight:bold">Е⌡╬ 2</span>О╪ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Advertising</code> (Е╧©Е▒┼) Ф∙╟Ф█╝И⌡├Ц─┌Х©≥Д╦╙Ф∙ёГ┌╧Е⌡╬Г╩≤Е┬╤Д╨├ 200 Д╦╙Д╦█Е░▄Е╦┌Е°╨Г └ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sales</code> (Е█∙Д╫█: Е█┐) Е┘ЁД╨▌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">TV</code>Ц─│<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">radio</code> Е▓▄ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">newspager</code> Д╦┴Г╖█Е╙▓Д╫⌠Е╧©Е▒┼И╒└Г╝≈ (Е█∙Д╫█: Е█┐Г╬▌Е┘┐) Г └Е┤╫Ф∙╟Ц─┌Ф╞▐Д╦╙Ф∙ёГ┌╧Е⌡╬Ф┬▒Д╩╛И┐╫Г╩≥Е┤╨Д╨├ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sales</code> Х©≥Д╦╙Е▐≤И┤▐И─ Х©┤Ф≥╝И─ Ф°─Е╟▐Д╨▄Д╧≤ФЁ∙Г └Ф▀÷Е░┬Г╨©О╪▄Ф▀÷Е░┬Г └Х©≥Д╦╙Г╩⌠Ф·°Е╟├Е°╗Д╦▀Х┼┌Х╞╬Х╞╕Х╖ёЦ─┌Ф█╒Е▐╔Х╞²Х╞╢О╪▄Е°╗Ф╞▐Д╦╙Е⌡╬Д╦╜Г └Х⌠²Г╨©Д╩ёХ║╗Д╦─Д╦╙Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀О╪▄Е▐╞Д╩╔Г■╗Ф²╔И╒└Ф╣▀ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">TV</code>Ц─│<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">radio</code> Е▓▄ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">newspager</code>  Г └ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sales</code>Ц─┌</span></p>

<h2 id="2-Г╝─Е█∙Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓">2. Г╝─Е█∙Г╨©Ф─╖Е⌡·Е╫▓</h2>

<p>Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е│┤Х╝╬Д╦─Д╦╙Ф╗║Е·▀О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">Y=\beta_0 + \beta_1 X +\epsilon</script>

<p>Е┘╤Д╦╜О╪▄$\beta_0$ Е▓▄ $\beta_1$ Ф≤╞Д╦╓Д╦╙Ф°╙Г÷╔Е╦╦Ф∙╟О╪▄Е┬├Е┬╚Д╩ёХ║╗ <strong>Ф┬╙Х╥² (intercept)</strong> Е▓▄ <strong>Ф√°Г▌┤ (slope)</strong>О╪▄Д╧÷Х╒╚Г╖╟Д╦╨ <strong>ГЁ╩Ф∙╟ (coefficients)</strong> Ф┬√ <strong>Е▐┌Ф∙╟ (parameters)</strong>О╪▄$\epsilon$ Д╩ёХ║╗ <strong>Х╞╞Е╥╝И║╧ (error term)</strong>Ц─┌</p>

<p>Г╩≥Е╝ Ф╗║Е·▀ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Г └Д╪╟Х╝║Е─╪ $\hat \beta_0$ Е▓▄ $\hat \beta_1$О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▐╞Д╩╔Ф═╧Ф█╝Д╦▀Е╪▐И╒└Ф╣▀Ф°╙Ф²╔Г └И■─Е■╝И╒²О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\hat y=\hat \beta_0 +\hat \beta_1 x</script>

<p>Е┘╤Д╦╜О╪▄$\hat y$ Х║╗Г╓╨Е°╗ $X=x$ Г └Е÷╨Г║─Д╦┼Е╞╧ $Y$ Г └И╒└Ф╣▀Ц─┌И─ Е╦╦О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г■╗Е╦╫Е╜░Г╛╕Е▐╥ Б─°^Б─² Х║╗Г╓╨Д╪╟Х╝║Е─╪Ц─┌</p>

<h3 id="21-Ф°─Е╟▐Д╨▄Д╧≤Е▐┌Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║">2.1 Ф°─Е╟▐Д╨▄Д╧≤Е▐┌Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║</h3>

<p>Д╩╓ $\hat y_i=\hat \beta_0 +\hat \beta_1 x_i$ Х║╗Г╓╨Ф═╧Ф█╝ $X$ Г └Г╛╛ $i$ Д╦╙Е─╪И╒└Ф╣▀Г └ $Y$О╪▄Д╦■ $e_i=y_i-\hat y_i$ Д╩ёХ║╗Г╛╛ $i$ Д╦╙ <strong>Ф╝▀Е╥╝ (residual)</strong>Ц─┌</p>

<p>Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е╝ Д╧┴ <strong>Ф╝▀Е╥╝Е╧ЁФ√╧Е▓▄ (residual sum of squares, RSS)</strong> Д╦╨О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\mathrm{RSS}=e_1^2+e_2^2+\cdots +e_n^2</script>

<p>Ф┬√Х─┘Г╜┴Д╩╥Е°╟Е╝ Д╧┴Д╦╨О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\mathrm{RSS}=(y_1-\hat \beta_0 - \hat \beta_1 x_1)^2 + (y_2-\hat \beta_0 - \hat \beta_1 x_2)^2+\cdots + (y_n-\hat \beta_0 - \hat \beta_1 x_n)^2</script>

<p>Ф°─Е╟▐Д╨▄Д╧≤ФЁ∙Д╪ И─┴Ф▀╘ $\hat \beta_0$ Е▓▄ $\hat \beta_1$ Д╫©Е╬≈ $\mathrm{RSS}$ Ф°─Е╟▐Е▄√Ц─┌И─ Х©┤Х╝║Г╝≈Е▐╞Г÷╔О╪▄Д╫© $\mathrm{RSS}$ Ф°─Е╟▐Е▄√Г └Е▐┌Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║Е─╪Д╦╨О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">% <![CDATA[
\begin{align}
\hat \beta_1 &= \dfrac{\sum_{i=1}^n (x_i-\overline x\,)(y_i-\overline y\,)}{\sum_{i=1}^{n}(x_i-\overline x\,)^2} \\[2ex]
\hat \beta_0 &= \overline y - \hat \beta_1 \overline x
\end{align} %]]></script>

<p>Е┘╤Д╦╜О╪▄$\overline y\equiv \frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n y_i$ Е▓▄ $\overline x\equiv \frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n x_i$ Ф≤╞Ф═╥Ф°╛Е²┤Е─╪Ц─┌</p>

<h4 id="Д╬▀Е╜░Е╧©Е▒┼Ф∙╟Ф█╝">Д╬▀Е╜░О╪ Е╧©Е▒┼Ф∙╟Ф█╝</h4>

<p><img src="http://andy-blog.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/blog/2020-09-08-WX20200908-111130%402x.png" width="70%" /></p>

<p><span style="font-size:10pt"> <span style="color:steelblue;font-weight:bold">Е⌡╬ 3</span>О╪ Е╞╧Д╨▌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Advertising</code> Ф∙╟Ф█╝И⌡├О╪▄Ф°─Е╟▐Д╨▄Д╧≤ФЁ∙Ф▀÷Е░┬ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sales</code> Е┘ЁД╨▌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">TV</code> Г └Е⌡·Е╫▓О╪▄Е╕┌Е⌡╬Ф┴─Г╓╨Ц─┌Х©≥Г╖█Ф▀÷Е░┬Ф≤╞И─ Х©┤Д╫©Ф╝▀Е╥╝Е╧ЁФ√╧Е▓▄Ф°─Е╟▐Е▄√Е╬≈Е┬╟Г └Ц─┌Ф╞▐Ф²║Г│╟Х┴╡Г╨©Ф╝╣Д╩ёХ║╗Д╦─Д╦╙Ф╝▀Е╥╝О╪▄Ф▀÷Е░┬Ф╗║Е·▀Ф≤╞Е╞╧Х╞╞Е╥╝Е╧ЁФ√╧Е▓▄Е▐√Е²┤Е─╪Ф┼≤Д╦╜Г └Г╩⌠Ф·°Ц─┌Х©≥И┤▄Г └Г╨©Ф─╖Ф▀÷Е░┬Ф┼⌠Д╫▐Д╨├Е▐≤И┤▐И≈╢Е┘ЁГЁ╩Г └Ф°╛Х╢╗О╪▄Е╟╫Г╝║Е╝┐Е╞╧Е⌡╬Д╦╜Е╥╕Д╬╖Е▄╨Е÷÷Г └Ф▀÷Е░┬Г╗█Ф°┴Г╪╨И≥╥Ц─┌</span></p>

<h3 id="22-Х╞└Д╩╥ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║Е─╪Г └Е┤├Г║╝Ф─╖">2.2 Х╞└Д╩╥ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Д╪╟Х╝║Е─╪Г └Е┤├Г║╝Ф─╖</h3>

<h4 id="Ф═┤Е┤├Х╞╞Е╥╝">Ф═┤Е┤├Х╞╞Е╥╝</h4>

<p>Д╦─Д╦╙Д╪╟Х╝║И┤▐Г └ <strong>Ф═┤Е┤├Х╞╞Е╥╝ (standard error)</strong> Е▐█Ф≤═Д╨├Е╝┐Е°╗И┤█Е╓█И┤┤Ф═╥Д╦▀Г └Е▐≤Е▄√Ф┐┘Е├╣Ц─┌Ф┬▒Д╩╛Ф°┴О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">% <![CDATA[
\begin{align}
\mathrm{SE}(\hat \beta_1)^2 &= \dfrac{\sigma^2}{\sum_{i=1}^{n}(x_i-\overline x\,)^2}\\[2ex]
\mathrm{SE}(\hat \beta_0)^2 &= \sigma^2 \left[\dfrac{1}{n} + \dfrac{\overline x\,^2}{\sum_{i=1}^{n}(x_i-\overline x\,)^2}\right]
\end{align} %]]></script>

<p>Е┘╤Д╦╜О╪▄$\sigma^2=\mathrm{Var}(\epsilon)$Ц─┌</p>

<h4 id="Г╫╝Д©║Е▄╨И≈╢">Г╫╝Д©║Е▄╨И≈╢</h4>

<p>Х©≥Д╨⌡Ф═┤Е┤├Х╞╞Е╥╝Е▐╞Д╩╔Г■╗Ф²╔Х╝║Г╝≈ <strong>Г╫╝Д©║Е▄╨И≈╢ (confidence intervals)</strong>Ц─┌Д╦─Д╦╙ $95 \%$ Г╫╝Д©║Е▄╨И≈╢Х╒╚Е╝ Д╧┴Д╦╨Д╦─Д╦╙Е▐√Е─╪Х▄┐Е⌡╢О╪ Х╞╔Х▄┐Е⌡╢Ф°┴ $95\%$ Г └Ф╕┌Г▌┤Д╪ Е▄┘Е░╚Ф°╙Г÷╔Е▐┌Ф∙╟Г └Г°÷Е╝·Е─╪Ц─┌Е╝┐Е┘╥Ф°┴Е╫╒Е╪▐О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\hat \beta_1 \pm 2\cdot \mathrm{SE}(\hat \beta_1)</script>

<p>Д╧÷Е╟╠Ф≤╞Х╞╢О╪▄Д╦▀Х©╟Е▄╨И≈╢</p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">\left[\hat \beta_1 - 2\cdot \mathrm{SE}(\hat \beta_1), \hat \beta_1 + 2\cdot \mathrm{SE}(\hat \beta_1)\right]</script>

<p>Ф°┴Г╨╕ $95\%$ Г └Ф╕┌Г▌┤Д╪ Е▄┘Е░╚ $\beta_1$ Г └Г°÷Е╝·Е─╪ (Е°╗Ф┬▒Д╩╛Х┐╫Е╓÷И─ Х©┤И┤█Е╓█И┤┤Ф═╥Е╬≈Е┬╟Г╠╩Д╪╪Е╫⌠Е┴█Ф═╥Ф°╛Г └Ф┐┘Е├╣Д╦▀)Ц─┌</p>

<p>Е╞╧Д╨▌Е┴█И²╒Г └Е╧©Е▒┼Ф∙╟Ф█╝Г └Д╬▀Е╜░О╪▄$\beta_1$ Г └ $95\%$ Г╫╝Д©║Е▄╨И≈╢Д╦╨ $[0.042, 0.053]$Ц─┌</p>

<h4 id="Е│┤Х╝╬Фё─И╙▄">Е│┤Х╝╬Фё─И╙▄</h4>

<p>Ф═┤Е┤├Х╞╞Е╥╝Д╧÷Е▐╞Д╩╔Г■╗Д╨▌Е╞╧ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Х©⌡Х║▄ <strong>Е│┤Х╝╬Фё─И╙▄ (hypothesis test)</strong>Ц─┌Ф°─Е╦╦Г■╗Г └Е│┤Х╝╬Фё─И╙▄Е▄┘Ф▀╛Е╞╧ <strong>И⌡╤Е│┤Х╝╬ (null hypothesis)</strong>О╪ </p>

<p><span><center>$H_0:$ $X$ Е▓▄ $Y$ Д╧▀И≈╢Ф╡║Ф°┴Е┘ЁГЁ╩</center></span></p>

<p>Е▓▄ <strong>Е╓┤Ф▀╘Е│┤Х╝╬ (alternative hypothesis)</strong>О╪ </p>

<p><span><center>$H_a:$ $X$ Е▓▄ $Y$ Д╧▀И≈╢Е╜≤Е°╗Д╦─Е╝ Г └Е┘ЁГЁ╩</center></span></p>

<p>Ф∙╟Е╜╕Д╦┼Ф²╔Х╞╢О╪▄Х©≥Е╟╠Г⌡╦Е╫⌠Д╨▌Фё─И╙▄</p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">H_0: \beta_1=0 \qquad \mathrm{vs.} \qquad H_a: \beta_1 \ne 0</script>

<p>Е⌡═Д╦╨Е╕┌Ф·° $\beta_1=0$О╪▄И┌ёД╧┬Ф╗║Е·▀Е╟├Г╝─Е▄√Д╦╨ $Y=\beta_0 + \epsilon$О╪▄Х─▄ $X$ Д╦▌ $Y$ Е╟├Д╦█Е├█Г⌡╦Е┘ЁЦ─┌</p>

<p>Д╦╨Д╨├Фё─И╙▄И⌡╤Е│┤Х╝╬О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Д╪ Ф▄┴Г┘╖Д╦▀Е╪▐Х╝║Г╝≈Д╦─Д╦╙ <strong>$t$ Г╩÷Х╝║И┤▐</strong>О╪ </p>

<script type="math/tex; mode=display">t=\dfrac{\hat \beta_1 - 0}{\mathrm{SE}(\hat \beta_1)}</script>

<p>Е╝┐Е╟├Ф°█Д╩▌Д╦─Д╦╙Х┤╙Г■╠Е╨╕Д╦╨ $n-2$ Г └ $t$ Е┬├Е╦┐О╪▄Е│┤Х╝╬ $\beta_1=0$Ц─┌</p>

<p>Д╫©Г■╗Г╩÷Х╝║Х╫╞Д╩╤О╪▄Е╬┬Е╝╧Ф≤⌠Х╝║Г╝≈Д╩╩Ф└▐Х╖┌Ф╣▀Е─╪Е╓╖Д╨▌Г╜┴Д╨▌ $\lvert t \rvert$ Г └Ф╕┌Г▌┤О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Г╖╟Ф╜╓Ф╕┌Г▌┤Д╦╨ <strong>$p$ Е─╪ (p-value)</strong>Ц─┌</p>

<h4 id="Д╬▀Е╜░Е╧©Е▒┼Ф∙╟Ф█╝Г └Г╩⌠Ф·°">Д╬▀Е╜░О╪ Е╧©Е▒┼Ф∙╟Ф█╝Г └Г╩⌠Ф·°</h4>

<p>Х║╗ 1 Ф▐░Д╬⌡Д╨├ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Advertising</code> Ф∙╟Ф█╝И⌡├Д╦╜И■─И┤▐Е╞╧Г■╣Х╖├Е╧©Е▒┼И╒└Г╝≈Г └Ф°─Е╟▐Д╨▄Д╧≤Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Г └Г╩├Х┼┌Ц─┌Е▐╞Д╩╔Г°▀Е┤╨О╪▄Д╦▌Е╝┐Д╩╛Г └Ф═┤Е┤├Х╞╞Е╥╝Г⌡╦Ф╞■О╪▄ГЁ╩Ф∙╟ $\hat \beta_0$ Е▓▄ $\hat \beta_1$ Г └Е─╪Е╬┬Е╓╖О╪▄Ф┴─Д╩╔ t Г╩÷Х╝║И┤▐Д╧÷Е╬┬Е╓╖Ц─┌Е╕┌Ф·° $H_0$ Д╦╨Г°÷О╪▄Е┤╨Г▌╟Х©≥Ф═╥Г └Е─╪Г └Ф╕┌Г▌┤Е┤═Д╧▌Д╦╨И⌡╤Ц─┌Е⌡═Ф╜╓О╪▄Ф┬▒Д╩╛Е▐╞Д╩╔Е╬≈Е┤╨Г╩⌠Х╝╨ $\beta_0 \ne 0$ Е▓▄ $\beta_1 \ne 0$Ц─┌</p>

<p><span style="font-size:10pt"> <span style="color:steelblue;font-weight:bold">Х║╗ 1</span>О╪ Е╞╧Д╨▌ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Advertising</code> Ф∙╟Ф█╝О╪▄И■─И┤▐Е╞╧Г■╣Х╖├Е╧©Е▒┼И╒└Г╝≈Г └Ф°─Е╟▐Д╨▄Д╧≤Е⌡·Е╫▓Ф╗║Е·▀Г └ГЁ╩Ф∙╟Ц─┌Г■╣Х╖├Е╧©Е▒┼И╒└Г╝≈Ф╞▐Е╒·Е┼═ $1000$ Г╬▌Е┘┐О╪▄И■─И┤▐Е╒·Е┼═Г╨╕ $50$ Д╦╙Е█∙Д╫█Ц─┌(<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sales</code> Е▐≤И┤▐Ф≤╞Д╩╔Д╦─Е█┐Е▐╟Д╦╨Е█∙Д╫█О╪▄Х─▄ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">TV</code> Е▐≤И┤▐ Ф≤╞Д╩╔Д╦─Е█┐Г╬▌Е┘┐Д╦╨Е█∙Д╫█Ц─┌)</span></p>

